<figureCitation id="8442B0DAE022F7A973922CE8556EF477" captionStart="Figure 4" captionStartId="F5" captionText="Figure 4. Thismia belumensis Siti-Munirah &amp; Suhaimi-Miloko A habitat B T. belumensis growing in leaf litter, FRI 94758 C habit of the young flowering plant and the young fruit of T. belumensis D fruits of T. belumensis, in-situ (Photos by A-C Siti-Munirah MY D Suhaimi-Miloko Z)." figureDoi="10.3897/phytokeys.172.59336.figure4" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/510452" pageId="0" pageNumber="121">4</figureCitation>
