<figureCitation id="62EA065E2BB0FE2E45B5DA4D91204B61" captionStart="Figure 5" captionStartId="F6" captionText="Figure 5. Other Thismia species found in the same area as T. belumensis A Thismia sp. 1, undescribed species B top view of Thismia sp 1. showing the annulus and tepals C Thismia javanica D top view of T. javanica showing the annulus and tepals (symmetrical flower) (All photos by Siti-Munirah MY)." figureDoi="10.3897/phytokeys.172.59336.figure5" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/510453" pageId="0" pageNumber="121">5</figureCitation>
